{"tid":2442884,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人信前世今生？","createTime":"2021-03-11T16:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T16:12:18.000Z","uid":152527,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3258f1cd3232dcae40f1dcd194dfff2540282913","tid":2442884,"uid":152527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:14:55.000Z","msg":"大家會唔會信前世今生，會唔會同自己既伴侶第一次相識時 有久別重逢感覺？ <br />\n<br />\n我網上識左一位行家朋友 約半年以 telegram 傾計，感覺似同識左好耐朋友傾計。傾左約三個月有日夢見同呢位網友發生關係。個夢好真，但奇怪在明明同位網友未見過面。之後第一次約正式見面感覺大家識左好耐既感覺。正式見面一個月 就真係同該位網友一齊左 而且發生關係<br />\n<br />\n可能有人話睇完av 都夢見同位女優發生關係<br />\n<br />\n但我同呢位網友既經歷 感覺前世今生因果。大家對伴侶有咁既感覺嗎"},{"pid":"64c9b30648850c14ea84cd3dddce004df3c82642","tid":2442884,"uid":283903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"021c575f1c22dd654160e680cd27fd84e3515251","tid":2442884,"uid":104182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"喺邊個網識"},{"pid":"5a5651ef292b0b8210b2e50bb1591317a57b9497","tid":2442884,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"發下夢都好既, 有夢最美"},{"pid":"7e8cead408d05dac4a55b6761ac61c2d3e2b5e0e","tid":2442884,"uid":258026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"夢裡甚麼都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe5cb4805fc81c0ba01198b029d65d9f31c966e","tid":2442884,"uid":307877,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YifL08V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYifL08V.jpg&h=20eb08c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df1ed5e447e90f7022c67b69888c47eb8f1ef802","tid":2442884,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"鳩痕就鳩痕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fa17193011d9487b8f2f7f108d